<item>
            <title>[SOLR-5261] can&apos;t update current trunk or 4x with 4.4 or earlier binary protocol</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-5261</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Seems back compat in the binary protocol was broke broke sometime after 4.4&lt;/p&gt;</description>
